<p>Adding a feature</p><p>Add features being used for your release. 
  </p> 
	  
		<ul> 
		   
			  The release must be created. 
			  
		   
		 
	 </ul> 
	  
		<p> Add each feature for the release to
		  the Features tab. This tab is available to your team members and they can refer
		  to it to find feature-specific information. 
		</p> 
	  
	  
		 
		   In 
			 My Products, expand the desired product. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Click the desired release. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Click 
			 Features. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Click 
			 Create a new feature. 
		   
		 
		 
		   Enter a name and description for the feature. 
		   
		 
		 
		   Select the release in which the feature is introduced. 
		   
		 
		 
		  (Optional) Select assets associated with the feature. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Click 
			 Save. 
		   
		 
	  
	  
		<p> The feature is added. 
		</p> 
	  
	 

		<p>Repeat this task for each feature in
		  the release. 
		</p> 
	  
  